 />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab70373e678628d31b35d54af19ed5ecd8798f6","tid":89794,"uid":5258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:22:50.000Z","msg":"應該咁講<br />\n商場同旺區係拖住gip嘅大陸人<br />\n其他區係新移民<br />\n總括黎講成個香港都係大陸人"},{"pid":"6c0b3c041ace4c19c62eb5cd3b332d324b6fc5ce","tid":89794,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:29:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該咁講<br />\n商場同旺區係拖住gip嘅大陸人<br />\n其他區係新移民<br />\n總括黎講成個香港都係大陸人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港人變左小數族群。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f0da52fc51e42da0128e30bbf66adab38e6b43","tid":89794,"uid":34284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:30:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港無一忽冇蝗</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中環嗰邊始終好過九龍新界，有多d鬼佬，唔洗日日對住成班中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當納粹來抓共產黨人<br />\n我保持沉默<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;我不是共產黨員<br />\n<br />\n當他們關押社會民主黨人<br />\n我保持沉默<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;我不是社民黨員<br />\n<br />\n當他們來抓工會會員<br />\n我沒有抗議<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;我不是工會會員<br />\n<br />\n當他們來抓猶太人<br />\n我保持沉默<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;我不是猶太人<br />\n<br />\n當他們來抓我時<br />\n再也沒人為我說話了<br />\n<br />\n第日中環全部都係蝗國人後悔太遲"},{"pid":"5ea9ca04b7942f51fa561490c0970221eaa73cd9","tid":89794,"uid":32081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:33:25.000Z","msg":"2015年起冇去過旺角, 班FD約旺角就唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nD SALES又冇禮貌, 個環境又差, D廢老係街中間大大聲播小蘋果係到鳩跳舞, 諗起都嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e8159ae4e